ai.nuralogix.anurasdk.face

Interface FaceTrackerAdapter


  • public interface FaceTrackerAdapter
    Face tracker interface accepted by Nura SDK, it would be used in face tracker pipe, to track face and give face points from video frame. The implementation of the interface should adapt different face tracker' APIs to the same this interface.
